      },
      "description": "Value of cargo aboard hulls currently serving as warehouse storage (ship symbols listed in storage_operations.storage_ships for RUNNING ops), marked to best-known bid. At an era reset, stored goods are a TOTAL LOSS \u2014 this number is pure downside risk parked in warehouse hulls, not banked profit.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
